metadata.description:
Hojae presents thoughts around a possible demo for the Monty system and a review of other SOTA vision AI systems that we may compare against in an upcoming paper.

00:00 Introduction and Overview
01:00 Research Meeting Insights
05:30 Pose Estimation Methods
39:52 Exploring Monty's Learning Modules
44:14 Comparing Monty to Other Systems
